social_posts.post_text: POV: Waiting for your call vs. On the call
I’m hereeeee!!!!💜💜💜
Backstage conceitedness💚💁🏽‍♀️

My best friend, cheerleader, confidant, sweet tooth twin, and big sister was welcomed into heaven a year ago today. I miss her with every ounce of my soul. 

The impact she has had on my life and the lives of other continues on each and everyday. I am so lucky I got to experience her warm and confident presence. Her endless smiles and warm (and tight) hugs. Not to mention her infectious laugh. I will never forget how deeply she cared for me and gave me a safe place to turn to. And though she may not physically be here, I know that her care and guidance surrounds me from above🤍 I am happy that you have found your peace. 

Constantly on my mind and forever in my heart🤍 I love you and I miss you, Cheslie. 

#CheslieKryst
#ILoveYou
#Healing
#AlwaysinMyHeart
